title: FMT from 2-month old WT animals treated with vancomycin
DNA_extraction_kit: QIAamp Fast DNA Stool Mini Kit
design_description: DNA was isolated from one mouse stool sample pellet using the Qiagen FAST DNA stool mini kint following the manufacturers protocol. Isolated DNA was quantified by Qubit. Pooled libraries were sequenced on Illumina NovaSeq 6000 ensuring 70 million reads, each 150 base pair long.
